Furries are cute green aliens that love to visit strange planets and then stroll about oblivious to the dangers around them. 
Tap and swipe pinballs, ropes, logs, crates, carts, switches, fans and all sorts of other items to help create a safe path to the exit. 
Make sure you keep the Furries safe from strange galactic creatures, spikey pits, huge explosions, giant drops and the evil Furax.
